						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				
				<p class="shipping-policy-modern__text" style="font-size: 13px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-secondary, #e9e9e9); padding-top: 20px;">
					<em>This policy may be updated over time without prior notice. The latest version will always be published on our official website. In the event of a dispute, the final decision belongs to the seller based on the terms published at the time the order was placed.<br>Last updated: May 2026</em>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

